 information about them\u200A \u2014 \u200Aanything from subscribing to newsletters and discovering good blogs in that space, to attending meetups and conferences."), mdx("p", null, "One of the best ways to stay informed is by building a network of \u201Csocial gateways\u201D, people who are well connected in the communities you want to watch but that are also far enough outside your usual network that you are hearing about new things. Then, when a particularly compelling idea surfaces, you will hear about it early."), mdx("p", null, "Some communities are far more likely to produce winning ideas than others. In his classic work ", mdx("a", _extends({
